<Pnumber><CommentaryRef Ref="key-a1"/>66</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<Text>No person is entitled to council tax reduction if that person’s capital exceeds £16,000.</Text>
</P1para>
</P1></P1group></Chapter></Part></Body></Secondary><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-a1" Type="I"><Para><Text><CitationSubRef SectionRef="regulation-66" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/regulation/66" id="cnh7oncs4-01092">Reg. 66</CitationSubRef> in force at 1.4.2022, see <CitationSubRef SectionRef="regulation-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2021/249/regulation/1" CitationRef="cnh7oncs4-01089" Operative="true" id="cnh7oncs4-01093">reg. 1</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary></Commentaries></Legislation>